t(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>Tenderhearts Healthcare Staffing leads the way in healthcare workforce solutions, offering a comprehensive array of allied clinician specialties and assignment options, including permanent placement, travel, temporary, locum tenens, and per diem allied staffing. Our tailored allied medical staffing services and workforce solutions are crafted exclusively to suit your company\u2019s unique needs. Through a rigorous screening, interviewing, and quality assurance process, our allied staffing professionals meticulously match you with suitable candidates.<\/p><p><strong>Full-Service Allied Workforce Solutions<\/strong><\/p><p>Tenderhearts Healthcare Staffing sources qualified allied health professionals from the DMV Metropolitan area, covering North Carolina, Delaware, Pennsylvania, and New Jersey, for various settings.<\/p><p><strong>Physical Therapists<\/strong><\/p><p>We specialize in delivering qualified Physical Therapists (PT) and Physical Therapist Assistants to diverse clinic settings. Our team recognizes the crucial role PTs and PTAs play in preventive care, rehabilitation, and treatment for patients with chronic conditions and illnesses.<\/p><p><strong>Occupational Therapists<\/strong><\/p><p>Our recruiters and account managers understand the importance of sourcing the right Occupational Therapist (OT) or Certified Occupational Therapist Assistant for your travel therapy needs. We prioritize understanding your company culture to ensure we deliver the perfect fit for your population\u2019s requirements. We seek OTs or COTAs with the ideal blend of hands-on experience for both in-person and telehealth treatments.<\/p><p><strong>Speech Language Pathologists<\/strong><\/p><p>Our network of Speech Language Pathologists (SLP) is diverse and skilled. Collaborate with Tenderhearts Healthcare Staffing to invest in your patients\u2019 needs by bringing therapists aligned with your goals. Our SLPs are adept at working in various settings, employing both in-person and telehealth visits. In today\u2019s landscape, the ideal SLP candidate possesses competence, training, and years of experience beneficial to your company and the patients they serve.<\/p><p>For more information, please contact us at <a href=\"tel:+1 (866) 700-8442\">+1 (866) 700-8442<\/a> or email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@thhcs.com\" target=\"_new\">info@thhcs.com<\/a>, or fill out our information request form below. We will promptly respond to your inquiry.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Allied Staffing Allied Staffing Tenderhearts Healthcare Staffing leads the way in healthcare workforce solutions, offering a comprehensive array of allied clinician specialties and assignment options, including permanent placement, travel, temporary, locum tenens, and per diem allied staffing. Our tailored allied medical staffing services and workforce solutions are crafted exclusively to suit your company\u2019s unique needs. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-2434","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.thhcs.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2434","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.thhcs.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.thhcs.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/